<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Pull Requests over Time</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/code/api/v2/dashboard/pr-issues-over-time"}></MethodEndpoint>



Returns the count of the different pull request statuses
(Failed, Resolved (Failed and was blocking issues were resolved) and Passed) per day for the last 30 days. 
You can set the `repositories` and `startDate` parameters in the request body to filter the results.<br/>
